Steven H. Collis

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Steven H. Collis


Born
1961/1962 (age 55–56)[1]
South Africa


Title
Chairman, president and CEO, AmerisourceBergen


Predecessor
R. David Yost


Successor
incumbent


Steven H. Collis (born 1961) is an American businessman, the chairman, president and chief executive officer (CEO) of AmerisourceBergen.[2][3][4][5]
Collis was born in South Africa.[4]
