Insider Activity


Individual




Steven H. Collis



Mr. Steven H. Collis, CPA, is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at AmerisourceBergen Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at MWI Veterinary Supply, Inc. Mr. Collis was previously employed as President by AmerisourceBergen Drug Corp., an Independent Director by Thoratec Corp., President-Specialty Group by Bergen Brunswig Corp., General Manager by ASD Specialty Healthcare, Inc., a Member by Johannesburg Stock Exchange, and General Manager & Principal by Sterling Medical Services LLC. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of the Witwatersrand.



