Steven H. Collis 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman, President and Executive Officer Chief at AMERISOURCEBERGEN CORP, Steven H. Collis  made $9,978,176 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,234,231 was received as a salary, $1,330,783 was received as a bonus, $2,680,003 was received in stock options, $4,019,981 was awarded as stock and $713,178 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


